   Arima, Kurumi; Kyogoku, Daisuke; Nakahama, Naoyuki; Isagi, Yuji, Kyoto Univ, Grad Sch Agr, Forest Biol, Kyoto, Japan.
   Kyogoku, Daisuke, Tohoku Univ, Grad Sch Life Sci, Sendai, Miyagi, Japan.
   Nakahama, Naoyuki, Univ Tokyo, Grad Sch Arts \& Sci, Plant Evolut \& Biodivers, Tokyo, Japan.
   Suetsugu, Kenji, Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Sci, Dept Biol, Kobe, Hyogo, Japan.
